    <h2><a href="https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/study/manual/foundations-of-the-restoration-class-preparation-material-2019/lesson-18-class-preparation-material-latter-day-saint-women-and-the-relief-society?lang=jpn">第18課：末日聖徒の女性と扶助協会<br>
        <br>
        <img src="https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/bc/content/shared/english/relief-society/images/rs-seal/RSSeal_jpn_color.jpg?lang=jpn"

          style="width: 1px; height: 1px;"><img src="https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/bc/content/shared/english/relief-society/images/rs-seal/RSSeal_jpn_color.jpg?lang=jpn"

